      "text": "<p>Treba da postaviš atribut <code>background-image</code> na <code>url(https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/css-cafe/beans.jpg)</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "const hasBackground = new __helpers.CSSHelp(document).getCSSRules().some(x => x.style['background-image'] === `url(\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/css-cafe/beans.jpg\")`)\nassert.isTrue(hasBackground)"
